 main fare at the Stade Olympique de la Pontaise.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4918729573245156e-26, \"text\": \"Lausanne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletissima\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Swede\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"a City Event\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"an esplanade\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"English\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 619}, {\"ngram\": \"Lake Geneva\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"the main fare\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade Olympique de la Pontaise\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Duplantis will be up against American Sam Kendricks, the silver medallist in Paris, and also Renaud Lavillenie, the 2012 Olympic champion and former world record holder who failed to qualify for what would have been his home Games.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\", \"score\": 0.7694257520239033, \"rank\": 0.29611994772297634, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kendricks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Kendricks\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kendricks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kendricks\"}, {\"begin\": 798, \"end\": 803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.26260607922686e-14,